subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Gymnastics
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Gabby Douglas, an irrepressibly animated 16-year-old, has rapidly blossomed into the main competition for Jordyn Wieber, the stoic 17-year-old gymnastics world champion.
